<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; }
    .container { background: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 4px solid #2d6a4f; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #2d6a4f; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Did you forget something?</h2>
    <p>We noticed you left some items in your cart at Fresh Harvest Grocery.</p>
    <p>Your fresh produce is waiting for you! Click the link below to complete your checkout before they run out of stock.</p>
    <a href="<%= checkoutLink %>" class="btn">Complete Checkout</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
